@startuml UC2_SearchSortFilterModels

title UC2 - Search / Sort / Filter Models (Simple Sequence)

actor User
participant UI
participant System
database Database

User -> UI : Enter search / select sort / filter
UI -> System : Request filtered model list
System -> Database : Query models with conditions
Database --> System : Return filtered list
System --> UI : Send filtered models
UI --> User : Display updated list

@enduml
